<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>LEGEND DRIVES - Ayodhya</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            /* Swapped to a luxury car interior background */
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.75), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.75)), 
                        url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503376780353-7e6692767b70?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop') center/cover no-repeat fixed;
            color: white;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
            padding: 50px 30px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
            max-width: 750px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
        }

        .logo-img {
            max-width: 320px; 
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.5));
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 3.8rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: #f1c40f; 
            letter-spacing: -1px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            color: #ffffff;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            color: #bdc3c7;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .btn-group {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column; 
            align-items: center;    
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .btn {
            padding: 18px 45px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 12px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            text-decoration: none;
            display: block;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 350px; 
        }

        .btn-book {
            background-color: #2ecc71; 
            color: white;
        }

        .btn-blue {
            background-color: #3498db; 
            color: white;
        }

        .btn-urgent {
            background-color: #e74c3c; 
            color: white;
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            filter: brightness(1.1);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0% { transform: scale(1); }
            50% { transform: scale(1.05); }
            100% { transform: scale(1); }
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; }
            h2 { font-size: 1.2rem; }
            .btn { max-width: 100%; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <img src="https://cdn.postimage.me/2026/05/03/file_000000007ddc71f4b1eacb7b10852390.png" alt="LEGEND DRIVES Logo" class="logo-img">

        <h1>LEGEND DRIVES</h1>
        
        <h2>अयोध्या शहर से ही पूरे भारत में किसी भी शहर में जाने के लिए बुकिंग करें</h2>
        
        <p>
            Welcome to <strong>LEGEND DRIVES</strong>. Here you can book vehicles to travel to any city in India starting from Ayodhya. <br>
            <strong>Soon, we will be available across all cities!</strong>
        </p>
        
        <div class="btn-group">
            <a href="https://wa.me/919369833831?text=Hello%20Legend%20Drives,%20I%20want%20to%20book%20a%20ride." class="btn btn-book">
                BOOK ON WHATSAPP
            </a>

            <a href="tel:+919369833831" class="btn btn-blue">
                CALL TO BOOK
            </a>

            <a href="tel:+917275306567" class="btn btn-urgent">
                URGENT CALL
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
